*chrony-2.4_pre1-r2 (29 May 2016)

  29 May 2016; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org>
  -chrony-2.4_pre1-r1.ebuild, +chrony-2.4_pre1-r2.ebuild,
  +files/chrony-2.4-r1.logrotate, -files/chrony-2.4.logrotate:
  Fix logrotate script

  Since grep -v may return a non-zero exit status even in the benign case, we
  need to just return 0 manually. Actual errors will still be reported
  normally
  since any output will trigger mail sending.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.3.0_rc1

